Notebook Computers




Does your company have a mobile workforce? Notebook computers are an essential tool for employees who are on the go. Notebooks are compact, lightweight, and portable. Equipped with a computer notebook, an employee in the field or on-site with clients can remain connected to the office and conduct... normal business activities. There are several types of notebooks available—from more robust, powerful desktop replacements to stripped-down, ultra-portable notebooks used primarily for Web browsing and light computing applications. The emergence of Ultrabooks has even provided a computing solution for mobile, power users. Ultrabooks combine powerful processing with a lightweight, ultra-portable body. Connection can help your business find the notebooks to meet your computing and mobility requirements while staying within budget.
We have an extensive inventory of computer notebook options from the top brands, including Acer, Dell, HP, Lenovo, Samsung, and Toshiba. Lenovo has a great line of notebook computers designed and engineered specifically for the business professional. The Lenovo ThinkPad T Series is stylishly thin and delivers excellent performance. Its advanced battery technology lets your employees work whenever and wherever they want.
In addition to the computer notebook options we have available, Connection also offers companion products and advanced technology services to improve your company’s mobile computing efforts. Our wide selection of notebook accessories includes carrying cases, docking stations, and batteries. We also have a trained staff of experienced technical experts to help provide your company with a better understanding of its network landscape. Our Mobility Services will help you successfully plan, design, and deploy your next mobile IT initiative. Learn how we can assist you with the security concerns inherent in a BYOD business environment.




