You Have a Lot to Offer Us, But What Do We Have to Offer You? 
We strive to be at the forefront of technology sales and services. But we can't do that without you leading our way to success. Working for us is more like being part of a family—a family of technology experts, Account Managers, customer service specialists, and more. If you're ready for a competitive benefits package, paid training, and supportive work and life programs, then Connection is the company for you. 







































































































































