	Small Business Technology Center - Connection











































Print page
E-mail page








Messages













Home>Small Business Technology Center











Small Business Technology
For 30 Years, Connection has been one of America's leading technology providers. Our mission is to serve businesses with trusted guidance, exceptional service, and innovative products throughout the IT lifecycle. Our customer-centric approach delivers all the benefits of large corporate IT procurement tailored to the needs of your growing business. We strive to create a foundation for long-lasting, rewarding partnerships, offering expert guidance, exceptional service, and innovative strategies to empower customers to make informed technology decisions.
With our online Small Business Resource Center you can:
• Place and track orders and shipments.
• Download technology whitepapers, podcasts, and webinars.
• Manage users and spending limits.
• Reorder frequently purchased items, like ink and toner, in 3 quick steps.



















Service & Warranty Plans— Go beyond limited manufacturer warranties. Through our collaborative approach to the design, deployment and support of technology, Connection has earned the reputation of trusted advisor to our customers.




Discounted Prices— We leverage our large corporate buying power and pass the savings on to you. Savings are automatically reflected once you login to the Small Business Center.




Special Buys—Our Small Business Email Alert grants you access to promotions, open box deals, refurbs, and more.





 
 














24 Hour "Quick Quote" Service—See a better price? Want to buy in quantity? Simply push your cart to us, or call for personal service, and we will send you a quote.




Flexible Financing Options— Leasing and 30-day net terms are extended to qualifying customers.




Superior Personal Service— Use a dedicated 800# to bypass our public phone queue. Talk with our knowledgeable New England-based specialists.






















Sign up for our Small Business Program today. Call 1.855.473.5681 



















