Overview

Welcome to the Connection Investor and Media Center. Whether you are an analyst, shareholder, or journalist, you have come to the right place for information on PC Connection, Inc. Here you will find facts about our Company, governance, press releases, financial results, annual reports, stock price data, and other useful information. And, if there is something you can't find, please contact us and we will be happy to help you.
Connection, Merrimack, NH, is a Fortune 1000 company with 2015 revenues of $2.6 billion. Connection has three wholly-owned sales subsidiaries: PC Connection Sales Corporation, MoreDirect, Inc., and GovConnection, Inc., headquartered in Merrimack, NH; Boca Raton, FL; and Rockville, MD; respectively. All three companies can deliver custom-configured computer systems overnight from our ISO 9001:2008 certified technical configuration lab at our distribution center in Wilmington, OH. In addition, the Company has over 2,500 technical certifications to ensure that we can solve the most complex issues of our customers.









