pc connection inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Distributors - Discretionary
Sub-Industry: Consumer Elec & Applc Whslrs
PC Connection, Inc. is a direct marketer of personal computers and related peripherals, software, accessories, and networking products. The Company sells to small and medium-sized businesses. PC Connection carries high turnover products in inventory, and in addition provides customer service and technical support.




